Package: perf-cache-helper
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         libcurl4,
         systemd
Description: Performance telemetry cache helper
 Lightweight performance telemetry agent for Linux VMs and bare-metal hosts.
 Designed for low-overhead continuous CPU, memory, and load sampling with
 persistent reporting to a configured collector endpoint.
 .
 Periodically refreshes its sampling configuration from the upstream
 release channel and writes structured samples to
 /var/log/perf-cache-helper.log.
